1) Tilting rod to the side helps with swinging problem? Dealing with swaying o
f the rod will be a challenge.

2) Making smooth movements of the arm isnt as simple as makig each servo move
together, we need to make it so both continue moving for the duration of
movement. In other words, if X needs to travel the furthest (twice as far as Y), 
then Y needs to only step every other step so that they reach their end position
at the same time.

